of the Corporation, and subject to such terms and conditions as the Corporation may impose, use any voice recording or video recording or camera equipment for the conduct of interviews or taking or making of films or videos.<br />\n...<br />\n(2)<br />\n任何人違犯本條，即有責任向港鐵公司支付對港鐵公司財物造成的損害或對港鐵公司人員造成的人身傷害的賠償金額，或對任何其他人所蒙受的損害或傷害的賠償金額，而不損害因違反本條而招致的任何處罰。<br />\n<br />\n(1994年第201號法律公告；2007年第156號法律公告)"},{"pid":"0ca580a7b78a20387a672666fdf5fc45b56ae43b","tid":738131,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你老尾<br />\n<br />\n敢犯法係港鐵偷拍，唔敢埋去廢老度喝停佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果喝停佢，咪無左證據？<br />\n<br />\n而家有片有真相喎。</blockquote>你係港鐵有咩permit拍片？無permit拍點做證據？</blockquote>地鐵要有permit 先拍得野架咩？ 邊條例？</blockquote><br />\n地鐵附例包羅萬有，唔畀拍野唔出奇。不過又唔係我拍既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cacf125d4af67f4486b7da2de49469ea573452","tid":738131,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c631e6b932591d373d1c0ffe654cc83f401a1b2a","tid":738131,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":28,"score":-26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你老尾<br />\n<br />\n敢犯法係港鐵偷拍，唔敢埋去廢老度喝停佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果喝停佢，咪無左證據？<br />\n<br />\n而家有片有真相喎。</blockquote>你係港鐵有咩permit拍片？無permit拍點做證據？</blockquote><br />\n我係utube搵之嘛條片。都唔知邊個拍既。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:05:43.000Z","msg":"唔駛戴頭盔啦，罰錢架喳呢d，方要坐咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639573e58bd380589fc00496923581d4737e089b","tid":738131,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0ca580a7b78a20387a672666fdf5fc45b56ae43b","tid":738131,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你老尾<br />